    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for the most budget-friendly way to get on the road? This well-worn vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it's seen better days and shows its age with noticeable wear, mechanical imperfections, and cosmetic issues. That said, it's a real opportunity for a handy buyer, a first-time driver on a tight budget, or someone looking for a project car to work on. At this price point, you're getting basic transportation with full transparency \u2014 what you see is what you get!",
      "price": 4500.0,
