    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2019 sedan in mint condition. The exterior is free of scratches, dents, and paint damage \u2014 the finish looks essentially new. The interior shows no signs of wear \u2014 upholstery, trim, and all surfaces are clean and undamaged. Mechanically sound with no known issues.",
